WEBVTT

00:10.788 --> 00:13.890
- It smells like feet in here.
- And whose fault is that?

00:13.924 --> 00:15.358
Whose fault is your face?

00:15.392 --> 00:16.726
Enough, you two...

00:18.262 --> 00:20.363
We should've left an hour ago.

00:20.397 --> 00:22.565
- Why do we have to go to grandma's?
- Theo, you love grandma.

00:22.600 --> 00:24.501
No, he loves Ashley Hammil.

00:24.535 --> 00:26.836
- Good luck with that, B.T. Dubs.
- Shut up, fart knocker.

00:26.871 --> 00:28.905
Nice! Classy.

00:28.939 --> 00:31.875
Tell me, Theo, what exactly is
a fart knocker?

00:31.909 --> 00:34.444
Kids!

00:34.478 --> 00:35.678
No! I wanna know.

00:35.713 --> 00:37.280
Is that how you're gonna
impress Ashley...

00:37.314 --> 00:38.515
- Oh.
- with your extensive knowledge...

00:38.549 --> 00:39.783
- Shut up!
- of fart-related insults?

00:39.817 --> 00:42.385
- Stop talking!
- Rachel, knock it off!

00:42.419 --> 00:44.988
Should I fart-knock it off, Dad?
because according to theo,

00:44.989 --> 00:45.655
- a fart-knocker...
- Gary...

00:45.689 --> 00:47.390
Both of you, stop it!

00:47.424 --> 00:48.591
You're gonna embarrass me
at your grandmother's

00:48.626 --> 00:50.360
- with all your bickering.
- Gary!

